<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Haptics</h1>
  <p class="lead">Meaningful touch feedback for emotional connection. Every vibration communicates.</p>
</div>

<section class="doc-section">
  <h2>Philosophy</h2>
  <blockquote class="philosophy-quote">
    "Haptics are not decoration—they're communication. Every vibration should feel intentional and human."
  </blockquote>

  <div class="principles-grid">
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Meaningful, Not Decorative</h4>
      <p>Every haptic should communicate something specific</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Warm, Not Clinical</h4>
      <p>Organic patterns over mechanical buzzes</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Subtle by Default</h4>
      <p>Reserve intensity for important moments</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Persona-Aware</h4>
      <p>Haptics reflect each character's personality</p>
    </div>
    <div class="principle-card">
      <h4>Respectful</h4>
      <p>Honor system settings and user preferences</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

